channel.title: Moparscape Server Status ( Need Help ) Someone please!
channel.description: Hey I need help with something :mad: and its making me really pissed. when I go on the server status page i try putting my server online it always says your server is offline.. I dont why it is saying that.. I have the little black box up which says the port 43594 is online and it says the same port on the server status box. I put the IP in which is working becuase my brother can connect on my other computer. The server is a 508 and I changed the thing on the server page to 508 server but its not working. I even put the ip as well.. Can somebody please help me with this problem I have like no one on this server exept me and my brother and I want more people on it. I got the no-ip up as well which shows all the green check and my port is checked black which means its online. someone please?

Yes.

mis·spell /mɪsˈspɛl/ Show Spelled[mis-spel] Show IPA
–verb (used with object), verb (used without object),-spelled or -spelt, -spell·ing.
to spell incorrectly.

http://dictionary.reference.com/browse/mis-spelt?&qsrc=[/quote]
[font=times new roman]-ed is a suffix that puts it’s root word in the past tense, ergo “misspelled” is “misspell” in the past tense. Either way you tried to make yourself look smart and me dumb and obviously failed. Perhaps next time. (;[/font]
